        <Parent_String>sewers by function [300131958], sewers (drainage structures) [300006122], drainage structures [300164058], hydraulic structures by function [300006112], hydraulic structures [300006073], single built works by function [300004894], single built works by specific type [300004795], single built works (built environment) [300004790], Single Built Works (hierarchy name) [300004789], Built Environment (hierarchy name) [300264550], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
      </Preferred_Parent>
    </Parent_Relationships>
    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sewers that carry industrial or residential liquid and solid wastes but not ground, surface, or storm waters. For parts of building plumbing systems designed to dispose of similar wastes, use "sanitary drainage systems."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000039651/Canadian Thesaurus of Construction Science and Technology (1978)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cloaca que transporta líquidos industriales o residenciales o basuras sólidas pero no aguas subterráneas, superficiales o de tormenta. Para partes de sistemas de cañerías de edificios diseñados para deshacerse de basuras similares, use "sistema de drenaje sanitario".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor riolen die vloeistoffen of vast afval afvoeren van industrieën of woningen, maar geen grond-, oppervlakte- of regenwater. Gebruik 'sanitaire afvoersystemen' voor delen van het afvoersysteem in huizen die voor soortgelijk afval zijn bestemd.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Kanal für Abwässer aus Industrieproduktion oder privaten Haushalten, aber nicht für Grund-, Oberflächen- oder Niederschlagswasser. Das System in Gebäuden, welches derartige Abwässer in die Kanalisation trägt, heißt "Hauskanalisation".</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>German</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000232/IfM-SMB-PK</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000122134/IfM Berlin</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>處理工業或家庭所排出之廢（汙）水及固體廢棄物的下水道，但不處理地下水、地面水或雨水。建築物中處理類似廢棄物之管路系統，稱為「衛生排水系統」。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000079740/AS-Academia Sinica data (2014-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
